  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Roll your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice!) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1596553680181-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1596553680181-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1596553680181-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1596553680181-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1596553680181-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 2-3 min or until they're tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596553689664-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596553689664-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596553689664-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596553689664-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596553689664-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the peas are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s] </strong>in a small bowl – this is your<strong> tangy garlic yoghurt</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596553701337-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596553701337-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596553701337-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596553701337-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596553701337-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>cooked peas</strong> to a low heat with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Mash until you're left with a coarse pea mash – these are your <strong>smashed chilli peas</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
