    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> diced chorizo</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until crisped</p>",
