    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs on high or until warmed through</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
